data.description: Feel the warmth when you step inside this well appointed home.  Three sided brick ranch with spacious split floor plan allows for entertaining and privacy for guests. Landscaping updates for added privacy with tranquil backyard oasis. Luxury vinyl flooring recently installed and interior painted. Snuggle up and read a book in the beautiful sunroom with plenty of natural lighting. A feast of updates recently completed including new lighting in many of the rooms. So much to offer in the way of activites including golf and the local YMCA. Within minutes to restaurants and shopping. Harrison High school district.  Don't miss the opportunity to call this picture-perfect setting home.
